## decodeUrlParameters() function

Decode the ExpositionValues from a given UrlParameters data set

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
declare function decodeUrlParameters<T extends Exposition$1<any>>(data: ExpositionUrlData): ExpositionValues<T> | undefined;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  data | ExpositionUrlData | data that got extracted from window.location.query |

<b>Returns:</b>

ExpositionValues&lt;T&gt; \| undefined


## Example

const values = decodeUrlParameters(...data)

exposition = setExpositionValues(exposition, values)
